Statements: The user interface felt intuitive to use
(For relevant users) I experienced few to no complications when installing and setting up the system
The provided robots facilitate for creating a diverse set of missions
I experienced few to no errors with scaling when adding a large number of robots
Based on my experience, I found the system to be useful to plan simple missions
I experienced few to no errors when executing the provided missions
I experienced few to no errors when creating new missions
I experienced few to no errors when modifying a mission
I found the syntax of the DSL to be simple to understand
I experienced few to no errors while using the web editor for the DSL
I experienced few to no complications with the communication between the robots
I found it useful to have different task allocation algorithms to choose from
I found it useful to be able to insert my own task allocation algorithm
Overall, the system facilitates well for extensibility
I would recommend this system to other users
I would recommend this system to other developers
Based on my experience with the system, I believe it is a good starting environment for robotics developers to add their own robots and implementations
